Repository is the layer that talks to database.

We don’t write SQL manually most of the time.
--------
WHAT JpaRepository Gives Automatically
Method	Purpose
save()	Insert / Update
findAll()	Get all
findById()	Get by id
deleteById()	Delete
count()	Count rows

